  "title": "Feature Request: Connector for Algolia Places widget",
  "body": "Hello! I'm hoping to customize the Algolia Places widget in my instantsearch.js project. (I need to add some behavior when a location is first set, and when the widget is cleared.) I've been able to customize other widgets (such as hits and refinementlist) using a connector, but no connector class exists for Places and it looks like I'll need to create a custom widget.\r\n\r\nApologies if this is the incorrect place to post a feature request; I was directed here by the note on [this page](https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/widgets/create-your-own-widgets/js/#introduction).",
